      "title": "Registrar service is two days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the crisis in the country, the Registrar General's Department has decided to restrict the services of all its regional and district offices from 8.30 am to 4.30 pm on Mondays and Wednesdays only.",
        "All services provided by the department, including the issuance of copies of land and birth, death and marriage certificates, are limited to those two days."
      ],
